hopobject.body: Languages ibuprofen/acetaminophen dosage in adults Elle hailed from California, whereas Smith comes from ‘a little village called Epworth, right bang between Doncaster and Scunthorpe’; both Elle and Smith are seemingly flighty on the outside, yet possess heart and a steely resolve. Although if there was any typecasting in that instance, it was the exception that proves the rule: Smith’s versatility is one of her key assets. ‘I like to play different characters, so I suppose I’m a bit of a chameleon,’ she admits.
